summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting electrical underground and surface rights distribution easements over portions of Parcels A, B, and E, City of Seattle Short Subdivision No. 83-549; A strip of land 18 feet in width in Government Lot 1, Section 2, Township 26 North, Range 3 East, W.M.; the north 15 feet and the west 15 feet of Lot 2 of Short Plat No. 09049 of Lot 5A, Block 4, First Addition to Lake Forest Park; the South 2.00 feet of Lot 5, City of Seattle Short Subdivision No. 83-337; the South 11 feet of Parcel A, and the east 15 feet of Parcels A and B of King County Short Plat No. 79-22; the east 114.92 feet of Lot 1, except the south 10.00 feet of the east 104.92 feet thereof, and the south 5.00 feet of Lot 2 of King County Short Plat No. 584009.
